ADS.Text1: Before the guide starts, I strongly suggest you play the game for one time by yourself!
ADS.Text2: The first 5 stages are easy, follow the only path, and with the NPCâ€™s instructions, you can quickly reach the labyrinth
ADS.Text3: Here I waste 5 mins for the first time I was here. The shortcut is: go left as always if you can.
ADS.Text4: Then you will reach the lollipop entrance, just jump over it and go straight ahead.
ADS.Text5: When you see a cat photo on the wall of the labyrinth, tap it again, the exit will appear.
ADS.Text6: Stage 8 is a little bit annoying, the final lollipop is hard to reach.
ADS.Text7: You can start with jumping at the sofa, and then the red and yellow lollipops, and then cat photo frame, cookie.
ADS.Text8: Rate Us 5 Stars And Download and enjoy endless fun with Grandma Escape Obby and Let's start your endless journey.
